	<summary>
		Navigate under your git repositories using a GUI client.
	</summary>
	<description>
		<p>
			QGit is a GIT repository viewer. It displays changes in a repository or a selected set of commit.
			This also includes visualizing the commit graph, showing information related to each commit, and 
			the files in the trees of each revision.
		</p>
		
	</description>
